I '''Harvey Weinstein''' (mibait Marzo 19, 1952) metung yang Americanung prodyuser pelikula ampong ehekutibung studiong pampelikula. Pikabaluan yang dili antimong metung kareng mitátag king [[Miramax Films]].<ref name="Kunz2007">{{cite book|author=William M. Kunz|title=Culture Conglomerates: Consolidation in the Motion Picture And Television Industries|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=OMD4bqQg4iAC&pg=PA15|accessdate=August 15, 2012|year=2007|publisher=Rowman & Littlefield|isbn=978-0-7425-4066-8|page=15}}</ref> Magsilbi lang pareung talapamuntuk (co-chairmen) ning kapatad nang i [[Bob Weinstein|Bob]] king [[The Weinstein Company]], ing kumpanya dang para king produksyon da reng pelikula, manibat 2005. Sinambut yang [[Academy Award]] king kayang pamag-produce king ''[[Shakespeare in Love]]'', at sinambut yang pitung [[Tony Awards]] para king produksyon da reng miyayaliwang drama ampong musical, yabae la reng ''[[The Producers (musical)|The Producers]]'', ''[[Billy Elliot the Musical]]'', ampong ''[[August: Osage County]]''.<ref name="Klinger2006">{{cite book|author=Barbara Klinger|title=Beyond the Multiplex: Cinema, New Technologies, and the Home|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=rg0WX8Ic-BsC&pg=PA212|accessdate=August 15, 2012|date=March 13, 2006|publisher=University of California Press|isbn=978-0-520-24586-0|page=212}}</ref>

